How to create pv using hostpath
================================
when you need local volume of work node. then we have two way.

1) hostpath
2) local path

IQ) difference between local and hostpath?
   => In hostpath api create folder automatically where local not. in local volume you will get volume only where you want like node1. then when your 
      container run on node2. it will not get folder ther.

hostpath volume => when you application required local volume in readonly mode from work-node.(from node where container running.)


